data.value:
Welcome to my Custom Program - Street Fighter You might need to use the keys on the keyboard to play: - Left and right key to move backward and forward for player 1. - J and L key to move backward and forward for player 2. - A, S key to throw punches for player 1. - B, N key to throw punches for player 2.
Features upgraded by Tran Hoang Duy Linh - 104222060 Swinburne University of Technology The program is inspired by: https://github.com/mooict/Street-Fighter-Demo-MOO-ICT
